# ::tok A friend shared months ago her 19 - year - old drafted Ukrainian son felt forced to fight separatists , fearing death with no choice .

    :ARG0 (p / person~1
        :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91~1

                :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91~13
                    :ARG1 p
                    :ARG2 (s3 / son~13))
                :ARG1-of (d2 / draft-02~11)
                :age (t2 / temporal-quantity~8
                    :quant 19~6
                    :unit (y / year~8))
                :mod d2)

                :ARG2 (f3 / fight-01~17
                    :ARG0 p2
                    :ARG1 (s / separatist~18))))
        :op2 (f / fear-01~20
            :ARG0 p2
            :ARG1 (d / die-01~21
                :ARG1 p2
                :manner (c / choose-01~24
                    :ARG0 p2
                    :polarity -~23
                    :polarity -~25))))
    :rel (c2 / country~12
        :name (n / name~12
            :op1 "Ukraine"~12))
    :time (b / before~22
        :quant (m2 / multiple~3
            :op1 (t / temporal-quantity~3
                :quant 1~0
                :unit (m / month~3)))
        :op1 (n2 / now~25)))
